### Create Vehicle
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/vehicles/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000",
  "plateNumber": "ABC-123",
  "make": "Toyota",
  "model": "Camry",
  "year": 2020
}

### Get All Vehicles
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/vehicles/

### Get Vehicle by ID
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/vehicles/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000

### Get Vehicles by Customer
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/vehicles/customer/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000

### Update Vehicle
PUT http://localhost:4000/api/v1/vehicles/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "plateNumber": "XYZ-789",
  "make": "Honda",
  "model": "Civic",
  "year": 2021
}

### Delete Vehicle
DELETE http://localhost:4000/api/v1/vehicles/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000